Why Kapalua Bay Villas:  Kapalua Resort is surrounded by 22,000 acres of natural wonder. Situated between two wild life preserves, Kapalua is home to a variety of tropical birds, exotic plants, fish, and giant sea turtles. During the months of January through April, Kapalua Bay and surrounding waters are playgrounds for an abundance of whales and their young. The Unique Benefits at this Villa:  Walking distance to world class beaches, championship golf courses, tennis, dozens of restaurants, and shopping, Kapalua resort offers something for everyone. For many, the Plateau is quintessential Montréal. Spiral staircases, bagels, Arcade Fire – it all started here in this rich and vast neighbourhood north of downtown. By day, kids play in the parks and friends debate politics in cafés; by night, restaurants and bars teem with people.

You will be only one block away from the famous Hospital Sant Pau, also a masterpiece from Gaudi, with its astonishing exposed-bricks construction and the charming Paseo Gaudí, one the most beautiful streets in Barcelona to enjoy walking, as no cars are allowed and plenty of shops, bars and restaurants offer the best of the local food throughout many terraces. You will be located in an centric well connected area, with the city’s finest restaurants.
